This repository is a derivative work built on Time-Causal VAE:
    https://github.com/justinhou95/TimeCausalVAE
    Paper: "Time-Causal VAE: Robust Financial Time Series Generator",
           arXiv:2411.02947
which is distributed under the Apache License, Version 2.0.

The upstream Time-Causal VAE source is INCLUDED UNMODIFIED, specifically:
    src/tsvae/            (the Time-Causal VAE package)
    src/evaluations/      (upstream evaluation suite)
    src/experiments/      (upstream experiment utilities)
    configs/, notebooks/ example decks, and trained_models/ shipped upstream

New original work added in this repository, and likewise licensed under the
Apache License, Version 2.0, is:
    portfolio_scenarios/                       scenario-tree generation layer
    notebooks/rolling_backtest_train.ipynb     rolling-window training pipeline

The added layer turns the Time-Causal VAE into a scenario-tree generator for a
two-stage stochastic portfolio optimizer; it does not modify any upstream file.
